Super 80 service —
With the latest technology and its carefully
designed interior, the Super 80 offers many
special features and enhancements normally
found only in widebody aircraft. Combine the
comfort of the Super 80 with American's
number one service and you've got an
unbeatable combination.
Pre-reserved seating. When you make
your flight reservations, we can reserve the
seat you want up to 11 months in advance,
and hold it up to 30 minutes before
departure. And we can hold seats for
passengers with boarding passes up to
five minutes before departure.
Curbside check-in. At most of American's
domestic airports, you can check your bags
at curbside for delivery to your final
destination.
One-stop check-in. You can buy or pick
up your ticket, select your seat and get your
boarding passes in a single stop at any
American ticket counter or at most flight
departure gates.*
Round-trip boarding passes. When
you check in for your originating flight, we
can issue your boarding passes for all
connecting and most return flights on
American.
In-flight service. We serve you with
warmth, courtesy and efficiency all along the
way. Our professional flight crews work hard
to make sure every trip you take with us is a
pleasure.
On-time dependability and performance.
Month after month, American is an industry
leader in on-time performance. You can
count on us to get you where you are going
on schedule.
*Service provided for all American Airlines domestic flights and
available on most international flights.
A
We're AmericanAirlines.
Doing what we do best.
